(125, 1, '2014-03-05 14:16:04', '2014-03-05 14:16:04', 'This pages are intended to create a nice place where to better explore the value of information. I write this pages being confident that one day one of my friends, teammates or even myself will use at least some information for rapidly solving problems related to software or hardware issues.\r\n\r\nI try to give thouse answers to problems I remember occured to me. Here are solutions that worked for me and at some point if I don''t use them for a long period of time I pretty sure I''ll forget most part of them.\r\n\r\nI can say for this little project I''m the scrum master, the scrum team and also the product owner because I had the initiative and the ideea to develop this site. One of the main goals of this website is to keep track of things occurred to me along time in my day to day computer activity, creating thus  a common documentation form my work and my interested fields.\r\n\r\nI consider this pages a little guide for all those happent to arrive here when searching for answers.\r\n\r\nThis are my personal notes and I''ve chosen to store them like this because I know that computers are better than us people on remembering and I''m also grateful to all those posting answers to different problems occurred on different websites or forums. There are great communities and great peoples there!', 'Thoughts', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'thoughts', '', '', '2014-03-10 09:25:38', '2014-03-10 09:25:38', '', 0, 'http://localhost/oltsoft.ro/?page_id=125', 0, 'page', '', 0),
