(202, 1, '2014-03-10 10:28:32', '2014-03-10 10:28:32', 'Using your knowledge on software development and project management you can be your own manufacturer or service provider in your free  time. There are allot of domains that need so little knowledge when you see things clear, but before starting to effectively do something (in whatever domain : painting, design and clothing, interior and exterior, gardening, cooking delicious and healthy food, gymnastics and sports) you should read tools instructions and ask for little advice ( online or from known people).  Plan this king of  work for the week-ends  in advance by writing it down in your notebook.\r\n\r\nEither way is good for your health to rest your brain , eyes (in fact the whole body) after standing at your desk from six-ten hours per day. You''ll fill yourself with energy by doing this kind of activities but if you''re tired the best thing to do is to take a nap so when you''ll go back to work you''ll be fresh and powerful, capable to be very productive in software developing. Do not ever be discouraged if you don''t  implement all plans written down or don''t fit the timelines. Keep all viable plans  and implement incrementally all tasks  having an useful result for  your future. Always CREATE VALUE  for you or for all those around you, persevere and one day you''ll be appreciated!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Be your best manufacturer or provider', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '00emi', 'be-your-best-manufacturer-or-provider', '', '', '2014-03-11 08:47:44', '2014-03-11 08:47:44', '', 0, 'http://localhost/oltsoft.ro/?p=202', 0, 'post', '', 0),
