(229, 1, '2014-03-11 10:12:52', '2014-03-11 10:12:52', 'When moving/reconstituting a WP website  from an old database an a manually coping of old files if when accessing a particular page or other content from website you are redirected to localhost/xampp or other home location of your public directory then change permalinks to default, after that verify if pages are displayed correctly. If so, you can change the permalinks back to post type so the page url can be more suggestive.', 'Only the main page of WordPress website works', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '133-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-03-11 10:12:52', '2014-03-11 10:12:52', '', 133, 'http://localhost/oltsoft.ro/133-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(230, 1, '2014-03-11 10:13:29', '2014-03-11 10:13:29', 'When moving/reconstituting a WP website  from an old database an a manually coping of old files if when accessing a particular page or other content from website you are redirected to localhost/xampp or other home location of your public directory then change permalinks to default, after that verify if pages are displayed correctly. If so, you can change the permalinks back to post type so the page url can be more suggestive.', 'Only the main page of WordPress website works', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '133-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-11 10:13:29', '2014-03-11 10:13:29', '', 133, 'http://localhost/oltsoft.ro/133-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
